      < >     PPP BSD-Compress compression (NEW)
      < >     PPP Deflate compression (NEW)
      [ ]     PPP filtering (NEW)
      < >     PPP MPPE compression (encryption) (EXPERIMENTAL) (NEW)
      [ ]     PPP multilink support (EXPERIMENTAL) (NEW)
